{"id": 2228, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得，哪些面对面的社交礼仪移植到线上会有点水土不服？", "description": "你都发现过哪些不同交流方式中的微妙差异？（题图来自：视觉中国）", "record_count": 1813, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180314173435Kjoig1qTkVA6R2JI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-15T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 270856, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256147}, {"id": 270857, "content": "还好还好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256147}, {"id": 280591, "content": "zai？\nbuzai！！cnm。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315067}, {"id": 271120, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285966}, {"id": 271123, "content": "吃了吗？这句一说对方会瞬间感觉你是长辈的风格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689835}, {"id": 270871, "content": "收到请回复", "image": "img/option/option/20180316150402T4cKja7p2BueDAFG.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955239}, {"id": 270873, "content": "客气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287185}, {"id": 271130, "content": "在吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289626}, {"id": 271132, "content": "面对面讲话尽量谦虚让双方有面子有尊严。在线上就是以事实为证据直接讲明理由!以工作为重心无须留颜面。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289685}, {"id": 272419, "content": "真的觉得对动不动就发哭笑不得那个emoji的人喜欢不起来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1293817}, {"id": 271927, "content": "你开心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285939}, {"id": 270650, "content": "觉得上来就甩句话不太好，每次说个什么都要加上名字之类的称呼，被人觉得太严肃", "image": null, "praise_count": 108, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 270652, "content": "觉得“跟人说了句话之后 ta 当然要立刻回复我啊”，搞不懂微信上为什么可以一两个小时不理人的", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 273724, "content": "在 你好 和 您好 之间犹豫来犹豫去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1301036}, {"id": 270659, "content": "一定要打~波浪号才能表达轻松的语气", "image": null, "praise_count": 213, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 558339}, {"id": 270660, "content": "线上看不到表情，语气全靠猜。最重要的是，线上社交几乎不可能拆穿谎言。", "image": null, "praise_count": 166, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 49665}, {"id": 270661, "content": "网聊后遗症就是  跟人面对面聊天词穷时 总想跳表情包回应", "image": null, "praise_count": 379, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747017}, {"id": 270662, "content": "线上要连发100个哈哈哈才能说明自己真的在笑而不是敷衍", "image": null, "praise_count": 135, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919463}, {"id": 270663, "content": "微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 761178}, {"id": 270664, "content": "每个人对说话方的意思有不同的理解，害怕自己的意思被人误解而又无法好好解释", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285984}, {"id": 270665, "content": "带节奏的观点影响了太多人，网上交流只要用一点时下流行语就能让人觉得亲切有趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285984}, {"id": 270666, "content": "嗯嗯，微笑再见等表情，你（N）忙（M）吧（B）", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1285987}, {"id": 271435, "content": "当面怼时不生气，同样的话变成文字发出去却像是在骂人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 270668, "content": "微笑的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275111}, {"id": 270669, "content": "网络社交礼仪：“收到消息要马上回复。”\n真是的，我又不是Siri 。", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256134}, {"id": 270670, "content": "中国人特有（？）的问候方式“吃了吗？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278872}, {"id": 270671, "content": "想说一个反例，线上晚上结束说晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286048}, {"id": 270672, "content": "大部分回答都在说网聊和面聊的区别，标题不是在问礼仪水土不服的问题吗？\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983596}, {"id": 270673, "content": "先寒暄再说正事。线上有事直白说，不用Hi什么打招呼或问在吗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141063}, {"id": 270675, "content": "当跟朋友吐槽事情时，对方回复：嗯！！\n下次不聊了囧rz", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286069}, {"id": 270676, "content": "和别人聊天好累啊，我一般都不闲聊 或者就想说什么说什么，玻璃心请靠边…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278548}, {"id": 270677, "content": "见面不能说一大长串哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈表示自己真的很开心", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284091}, {"id": 270678, "content": "交换名片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237423}, {"id": 270679, "content": "最害怕80后领导用呵呵微笑脸表示愉快", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275882}, {"id": 270681, "content": "在吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294953}, {"id": 270682, "content": "在吗？（在你妹啊管我在不在有话直敲啊！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294953}, {"id": 270938, "content": "心里mmp 脸上笑嘻嘻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1287555}, {"id": 270683, "content": "凡是语音都不想听，尤其是几秒的，无法有效提取信息", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1286113}, {"id": 271451, "content": "略词，导致现实生活中讲话讲不清楚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290602}, {"id": 270684, "content": "你的网名＋生日快乐！", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212756}, {"id": 270686, "content": "说话前先发个表情看你在不在，还有就是，沉默往往意味很多表情全靠猜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498281}, {"id": 270687, "content": "语气助词必须带！\n不带觉得自己说话太硬\n带了又有点gay里gay气", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284705}, {"id": 270688, "content": "各种强撩", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178173}, {"id": 270689, "content": "宁愿发表情包打招呼也不愿说你好以防觉得太官方。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1196749}, {"id": 270690, "content": "我麻麻习惯把社交媒体当信件用，比如和我说话的句子前面会打“女女：”，而且每一段话都非常、非常的长，她还不会换行分段……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 870298}, {"id": 270691, "content": "线上emoji丰富，线下傻脸一个", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935385}, {"id": 270694, "content": "线上聊天 码完字一定要配表情 不然对方的情绪全靠猜 捉摸不透 不如面对面来的畅快感", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277972}, {"id": 270697, "content": "是是是", "image": "img/option/option/20180315152837u35XMtaCOqh7Bo1U", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1256147}, {"id": 270698, "content": "有人发“在吗？“我从来都是回“不在”的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660702}, {"id": 270700, "content": "表情包有很多，那又怎样，任何一个表情包都代替不了真实的想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270903}]}